Author: carpal
Content:
The amputee wasn't barred from the olympics. This particular set of prosthetics was banned.

That guy can still run in the olympics with any other set of prosthetic legs but this one. It was just deemed that these gave him too much of an unfair advantage.

Author: jslogan
Title: An example of a missed opportunity to attract new customers
Content: A simple example: The things we do aren't important. Our customers don't want the things we have to offer, they want the things they can do or achieve with the things we offer.  Food for thought.
